3. User Stories
User Story 1
 As a visitor, I want to see a clear navigation menu so that I can easily move between different sections of the site.
User Story 2
 As a recruiter, I want to see a brief introduction and photo on the homepage so that I can quickly understand who this person is.
User Story 3
 As a hiring manager, I want to see real projects with descriptions and tech stacks so that I can evaluate the candidate’s technical skills.
User Story 4
 As a visitor, I want to see a visual representation of skills so that I can quickly identify the candidate’s strengths.
User Story 5
 As a visitor, I want to easily find contact information so that I can reach out if I am interested.

